      <title>面向全球用户的社交媒体平台 X down - Down detector</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/social-media-platform-x-down-users-globally-downdetector-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据 DownDetector.com 报道，周四早些时候，社交媒体平台 X 和 X Pro 在全球范围内遭遇宕机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/social-media-platform-x-down-users-globally-downdetector-2023-12-21/</guid>
