    <item>
      <title>香港法院判处资深劳工活动人士的妹妹监禁六个月</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-jails-sister-veteran-labour-activist-six-months-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港一家法院周四判处一名亲民主工会领导人的妹妹六个月监禁，原因是在这座中国统治的城市正在进行的安全镇压期间，她从后者的家中带走了证据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-jails-sister-veteran-labour-activist-six-months-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 04:02:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国警告菲律宾通过对话解决南海紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-warns-philippines-resolve-south-china-sea-tensions-via-dialogue-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国外交部长王毅警告菲律宾通过对话解决中国认为两国关系在南海问题上的“严重困难”，双方船只之间的事件已升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-warns-philippines-resolve-south-china-sea-tensions-via-dialogue-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 03:14:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾指责中国在取消关税后实施经济胁迫</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-keeps-up-pre-election-trade-pressure-taiwan-with-tariff-cut-removals-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，台湾指责中国实施“典型的经济胁迫”，此前北京在下个月台湾选举前夕宣布结束对台湾部分化学品进口的关税削减，并称台北违反了一项贸易协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-keeps-up-pre-election-trade-pressure-taiwan-with-tariff-cut-removals-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 03:07:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国和日本在关系改善的情况下恢复高层经济会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-japan-resume-high-level-economic-talks-amid-improved-ties-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首尔外交部表示，韩国和日本将于周四举行八年来的首次高层经济会谈，这进一步表明随着两国因共同的地缘政治担忧而走得更近，两国关系正在改善。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-japan-resume-high-level-economic-talks-amid-improved-ties-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 02:54:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>寒流袭上海 迎来40年来最冷年末</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-cold-snap-reaches-shanghai-with-chilliest-year-end-40-years-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国金融中心上海将在12月创下四十年来最寒冷的时期，促使当局发布低温和大风警告，而北方城市则在与冰冻天气作斗争，预计下周才会缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-cold-snap-reaches-shanghai-with-chilliest-year-end-40-years-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 02:29:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国地震后仍有十几人失踪</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/dozen-still-missing-after-chinas-earthquake-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一晚间，甘肃省发生6.2级地震，仍有十几人失踪，网友质疑救援行动结束的速度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/dozen-still-missing-after-chinas-earthquake-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 02:18:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国将妈祖“和平女神”宗教作为台湾选举的武器</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-wields-peace-goddess-religion-weapon-taiwan-election-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾政府文件显示，中国共产党正在加强与台湾农村民间宗教团体的交流，试图在下个月的选举前操纵政治舆论，使之有利于北京。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-wields-peace-goddess-religion-weapon-taiwan-election-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 02:08:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼加拉瓜镇压加剧，第二位天主教主教入狱</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/nicaraguan-police-arrest-second-catholic-bishop-local-media-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位与当地教会领导人密切接触的消息人士在当地媒体报道后告诉路透社，尼加拉瓜周三逮捕了另一位天主教主教，使该主教成为在长期镇压中第二位被拘留的此类领导人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/nicaraguan-police-arrest-second-catholic-bishop-local-media-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 00:39:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈马斯和以色列提出要求，埃及寻求促成加沙停火</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/egypt-seeks-broker-gaza-ceasefire-hamas-israel-assert-demands-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国表示，正在就新的加沙停火和释放更多以色列人质进行“非常认真的”谈判，但达成协议的前景仍不确定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/egypt-seeks-broker-gaza-ceasefire-hamas-israel-assert-demands-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 00:13:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>批评人士称，美国对萨博的宽大处理对马杜罗来说是件好事</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-clemency-saab-is-boon-maduro-critics-say-2023-12-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析人士表示，委内瑞拉释放了 30 名美国和国内囚犯，以换取总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗 (Nicolas Maduro) 的重要盟友的自由，这为马杜罗在明年选举前增强政治实力提供了机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-clemency-saab-is-boon-maduro-critics-say-2023-12-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 23:07:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科罗拉多州选票案件为特朗普的提名运动增添了动力</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/colorado-ballot-case-adds-fuel-trumps-nomination-drive-2023-12-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[来自两个主要政党的捐助者和政治分析人士表示，这一裁决将激怒特朗普的政治基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/legal/colorado-ballot-case-adds-fuel-trumps-nomination-drive-2023-12-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 22:28:32 GMT</pubDate>
